{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"code":"RenderContext","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the composition point for the workflow tree.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Methods","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeOutputSink()","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeSink(of:)","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeSink(of:onEvent:)","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeStateMutationSink()","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/runSideEffect(key:action:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"metadata":{"title":"RenderContext","modules":[{"name":"Workflow"}],"roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:8Workflow13RenderContextC","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"WorkflowType"},{"kind":"text","text":"> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"WorkflowType"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/Workflow","preciseIdentifier":"s:8WorkflowAAP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Workflow"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"During a render pass, a workflow may want to defer to a child"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"workflow to render some portion of its content. For example,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a workflow that renders to a split-screen view model might"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to child A for the left side, and child B for the right"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"side view models. Nesting allows for a fractal tree that is constructed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"out of many small parts."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If a parent wants to delegate to a child workflow, it must first","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"create an instance of that workflow. This can be thought of as the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"model of the child workflow. It does not contain any active state,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it simply contains the data necessary to create or update a workflow","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"node.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The parent then calls ","type":"text"},{"code":"render(workflow:outputMap:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with two values:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The child workflow.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure that transforms the child’s output events into the parent’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Event"},{"type":"text","text":" type so that the parent can respond to events generated by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the child."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had previously rendered a child of the same type, the existing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"child workflow node is updated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had not rendered a child of the same type in the previous"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"render pass, a new child workflow node is generated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The infrastructure then performs a render pass on the child to obtain its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"Rendering","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" value, which is then returned to the caller.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://Workflow/documentation/Workflow/Workflow":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/Workflow","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/workflow\/workflow","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Workflow"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines a node in the workflow tree."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Workflow"}],"title":"Workflow","role":"symbol"},"doc://Workflow/documentation/Workflow/RenderContext/makeOutputSink()":{"title":"makeOutputSink()","url":"\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext\/makeoutputsink()","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Generates a sink that allows sending the Workflow’s output wrapped in an AnyWorkflowAction, allowing bypassing an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"intermediate action."}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"makeOutputSink","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Sink","preciseIdentifier":"s:8Workflow4SinkV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"WorkflowType","preciseIdentifier":"s:8Workflow13RenderContextC0A4Typexmfp","kind":"typeI